'''Tolkien & Co''' was a [[Tolkien Societies|Tolkien society]] in France.

==History==
Tolkien & Co was active from the late 1990s through early 2000s. It can be assumed it is now defunct as no recent internet presence or activities are known to exist.<ref>[http://fr.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Études_sur_J._R._R._Tolkien Études sur J. R. R. Tolkien] at French Wikipedia</ref>
